---
title: Casablanca Chicken & Roast Veggie Medley with Citrus Yoghurt
description: Cauliflower is one of those superstar veggies, always ready to do the heavy lifting in any meal. With its special nuttiness that comes out after roasting, it makes a hearty addition to this spiced chicken stunner of a meal.
